<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.6.10">
<l>karuṅkaṇtō kaimayiṟ pīliya ṇintu</l>
<l rend="indent">kaṭṭinaṉ kuṭutta pītaka vāṭai</l>
<l>yaruṅkala vuruvi ṉāyarpe rumā</l>
<l rend="indent">ṉavaṉoru vaṉkuḻa lūtiṉa pōtu</l>
<l>maraṅkaḷ niṉṟumatu tāraikaḷ pāyum</l>
<l rend="indent">malarkaḷvī ḻumvaḷar kompukaḷ tāḻu</l>
<l>miraṅkumkūm pumtiru mālniṉṟa niṉṟa</l>
<l rend="indent">pakkannōk kiyavai ceyyaṅku ṇamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When the herder with the form of a precious jewel</l>
<l rend="indent">–the lord, the unique one,</l>
<l rend="indent">with golden clothes donned well,</l>
<l rend="indent">tying on and wearing peacock feathers with dark eyes–</l>
<l>played [his] flute,</l>
<l>the trees, remaining [in place],</l>
<l rend="indent">seeing Tirumāl, standing on all sides,</l>
<l>released [their] blossoms that spread [their] star[-shaped] pollen,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] bent low [their] long branches;</l>
<l rend="indent">[as if] weeping and closing [the eyes].</l>
<l>[Such] is the merit they have done.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
